name: TimeMix3
description:
融合了多个模型，加入了一些自练的模型，拥有更好的背光效果，以及更强烈的光影质感，风格特征更明显，在暗处的表现惊人，线条上更利落

Combining multiple models and adding some self-trained models, it has a better backlighting effect, as well as a stronger light and shadow texture, and the style characteristics are more obvious, the performance in the dark is amazing, and the lines are more neat
